         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" xml:lang="grc" subtype="transcription" xml:id="elus0006.transcription" corresp="#elus0006.translation">
            <p>Ἡ ἀρέτῃ <expan><abbr>κ</abbr><ex>αὶ</ex></expan> σωφρο<lb break="no"/>σύνῃ κεκοσμη<lb break="no"/>μένη
               <orig>φθανε<unclear>υ</unclear><lb break="no"/><unclear>πην</unclear>πε</orig>
               <gap reason="illegible" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <orig><unclear>λσ</unclear></orig> <orig>πεν<lb break="no"/>θεραν</orig> οὐκ ὅλον 
               <lb/>ἔτος <unclear>με</unclear>τ᾽ α<unclear>ὐ</unclear>τὴν 
               <lb/>πλη<unclear>ρ</unclear><supplied reason="undefined">ώ</supplied><unclear>σα</unclear>σα Θε<lb break="no"/>οδώρα Ἐρασίνου 
               <lb/>ὡς τῷ <expan><abbr>Κῳ</abbr><ex>υρί</ex><abbr>ῳ</abbr></expan>
               <expan><abbr>ἔδο<lb break="no"/>ξ</abbr><ex>εν</ex></expan>
               <expan><abbr>μη</abbr><ex>νὶ</ex></expan> Πανέμ<supplied reason="undefined">ου</supplied>
               <lb/><num value="13">ιγ</num>
               <expan><abbr>ἰνδ</abbr><ex>ικτιῶνος</ex></expan>
               <num value="6">ϛ</num>
               <expan><abbr>ἔτ</abbr><ex>ους</ex></expan>
               <num value="498">υ<unclear>ϙ</unclear><supplied reason="undefined">η</supplied></num></p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="elus0006.translation" corresp="#elus0006.transcription">
            <p>Adorned with virtue and modesty... lived not a whole year with her Theodora,
                    daughter of Erasinos, as the Lord willed on the 13th of Panemos, 6th indiction,
                    year 498.</p>
         </div>
